{"type": "article", "id": 24963, "title": "在东京这间博物馆，你可以了解关于自行车的一切", "description": "自行车爱好者必去之地。", "date": "2016-04-05T15:50:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 34, "name": "自行车"}, {"id": 7137, "name": "东京"}, {"id": 25826, "name": "自行车博物馆"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 204, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160608132035aKzSGDetJTr6f9Oh.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>东京的 <a href=\"http://www.cycle-info.bpaj.or.jp\">Bicycle Culture Center</a>（自行车文化中心）成立于 1981 年，是一个独特的空间，<a href=\"http://www.spoon-tamago.com/2016/04/04/the-bicycle-culture-center-in-tokyo-is-a-museum-for-bicycle-lovers/\">在这里你能找到与自行车有关的所有东西</a>——超过 9000 本自行车主题的出版物、骑行服、旧轮胎、老式海报，还有罕见的零件等等，博物馆内充满了可爱的小细节。</p>\n<p>自行车博物馆原本位于科学博物馆（Science Museum）内，2013 年它独立了出来。在加藤住吉建筑事务所（Kato-Sumiyoshi Architects）和 TANK 建筑公司的设计和建造下，自行车博物馆新家落成，位于东京的千代田区。博物馆于 9:30——16:50 开馆（逢周一闭馆），是对外售票的，成人票为每人 720 日元，约 43 元人民币。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132021sSmpnKcGw8hbNyDx.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">以下所有照片都是 kentahasegawa 拍摄的</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606081320222FnTpz0By9eo1UlP.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59259259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">东京 Bicycle Culture Center  一角</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606081320220HNMWAhLRfO8Jl9y.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132023SIL8JimyN7wO43st.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">店内全是与自行车有关的小细节</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132023VisgJBj25ZYNxzHw.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>这里时不时会主办自行车主题的活动和演讲，还有一个庞大的资料库供民众查阅。对自行车爱好者来说，这是东京之旅的必去之地。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132024CWT4Ef3mzHLlihvq.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.859\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">自行车主题的活动与展览</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p>自行车文化中心的设计方之一是加藤住吉建筑事务所。这家事务所由两个人主理——加藤直樹和住吉かほり，他们分别出生于 1984 和 1983 年，设计范围很宽泛，有展厅、餐厅，也有办公空间，走得是简洁实用的设计风。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132024ebxLCMXPZ02t8qo1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">这是他们设计的办公空间：COWORKING SPACE CANVAS</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132025dXUQRSu86gJVPcFM.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">走得是朴实实用风</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132025d7Ll16OpeMyqS5Va.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">这是他们设计的展览空间 SCOPESCAPE HIBIKINO</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132026oVf5XTZIjuiw9AaK.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.505\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">SCOPESCAPE HIBIKINO 展览上的灯光投影</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132026LeF6rlSIoNyWBgdY.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.669\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">这是他们设计的餐厅： BAULETTO</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132027b5jxWJ0DPNdenrIU.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.494\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">BAULETTO 的外貌</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">自行车文化中心的另一个设计方是  TANK。与加藤住吉建筑事务所相比，TANK 规模要大一些，共有 14 位成员。他们的设计也更倾向于工业风：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132027IReoBC2jkbJh73Gl.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">这是 TANK 设计的 Blue Bottle Coffee Kiyosumi-Shirakawa Roastery &amp; Cafe</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132028jfVkzghLG5AOp2T1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Blue Bottle Coffee 的植物一角</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132029J7P3ScDid68nryqb.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132029UD2vbf5sWhISJM0d.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Blue Bottle Coffee</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132030OPpcDqQif6zxnehX.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">这是 TANK 设计的 DESCENTE BLANC Daikanyama 展厅</p></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132030CZHz0QYe4DEVX7O8.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132031tWm6r8A2ShX9HyTq.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132031aTs80tYyUNGO1Scd.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">TANK 做的这个售卖空间也很好看，巧妙地利用了反光：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132032VgKsaDo5y0OWfHkB.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606081320327Kd4f2pORbJLFMlX.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060813203343z082yDnUpItagq.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132033nNLFeMqyYZShuwVE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606081320342bheG3XmvOSPq89r.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608132034dmTFg4wbLzk6YeGJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><br></div>\n<p class=\"\">题图来源：<a href=\"http://www.spoon-tamago.com/2016/04/04/the-bicycle-culture-center-in-tokyo-is-a-museum-for-bicycle-lovers/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">spoon-tamago</a><br></p>\n\n\n"}